posts.post_title: Dual HOF Jennings Miscut Mecca T201 (SOLD)
posts.post_content:
This card is in my hands but it belongs to a good friend who wanted me to post it and take offers. Card has no creases and 2 strong corners and 2 average corners. Most likely a 3 or a 4 (maybe a 5 on a  good day)

1911 T201 Mecca # 39 Hughie Jennings / Ed Summers

Miscut with 2 images of Hall of Famer Hugh Jennings as shown. Other side is miscut as well as you can see the faint line to the right of Summer's throwing hand.

Make offers if interested. Thanks! Mike[IMG]http://www.net54baseball.com/attachment.php?attachmentid=176321&d=1421974061[/IMG]
